Description:
Ready for a Cobram "Block" Renovation?

The cottage on the front of the block has been rewired and restumped, but there is plenty left to do! No kitchen or bathroom remain, but the rooms are there awaiting your renovating flair! Description:
Room to Move, By The Murray!
Welcome to one of the most Magnificent lifestyle properties in the Cobram area. All set on approx. 1 & 3/4 acres, this block provides both rural and in town benefits and it must be inspected.
With a spacious 4 bedroom home that includes a large lounge & family room, there are 2 bathrooms, large study, formal dining and the large north facing sun room will be well received on inspection.
All bedrooms are fully carpeted and include BIRs, ceiling fans and bedroom 4 includes a sitting area & extra storage, with the main including WIR & en-suite. Ducted heating, evaporative cooling and wood fire heater in the formal lounge room will keep the home at the right temp all year around.
The open kitchen includes gas cooking, dishwasher, breakfast bar, plumbed fridge, pantry and plenty of bench & cupboard space. It all matches in well with the 9ft high ceilings and there's also the new security doors and NBN connection, all added bonuses at Catona Court...
Externally, there's the single garage and double undercover carport, plus you also receive the brilliant 21m x 8m shed (3.5m high) includes 3 phase power & concrete, 3 x bays and a 6m x 8m lock up area
There is town water, natural gas, domestic bore and the immaculate gardens and trees throughout set the scene beautifully for the upcoming spring & summer
This property must be inspected and with a motivated vendor who wont play games, you will be very impressed with this outstanding lifestyle property in arguably one of Cobram's best areas...Catona Court!
Contact Brad Campbell on 0416291112 or Peter Cardamone 0419204608 to book an inspection today!!

Description:
STUNNING PROPERTY WITH THE LOT
This home consists of 48Sq of under roof living with veranda surrounding
• Beautiful Atrium style entrance
• Gorgeous Tasmanian Ash timber flooring
South Wing consists of:
• Has three double bedrooms with BIR and ceiling fans
• Large family bathroom with corner spa, shower, vanity and toilet
North Wings consists of:
• Master with ceiling fans, huge WIR and large bathroom with french doors to decking area
• Separate formal lounge/theatre or games room
Centre of the home you have:
• Open plan kitchen/meals/family room with ceiling fans, French doors opening out to the entertaining area overlooking pool
• 6 metre long island bench with ample storage
• Large walk in pantry, dishwasher, 900ml gas stove/oven
• You will be comfortable all year round with reverse cycle split system unit and Coonara wood fire
• Great size laundry with loads of storage and bench top space. 2 x linen cupboards etc
• Electric hot water service
• There is an additional 11Sq Granny flat with reverse cycle split system unit, kitchenette and separate bathroom, tack room and workshop
• Double carport off granny flat
Externally the property offers:
• Established trees, easy to maintain gardens
• In ground pool, fully fenced
• 46.9 acres of land with sealed road frontage and sealed side road
• Excellent electric fencing throughout property
• 10 paddocks overall with polymaster watering troughs
• 5 bay machinery shed
• 40 x 40mtr Sand Arena
• Tie up wash area
• Garden shed, chook pen
• New cattle yard with crush and ramp
• Licensed irrigation bore
• Delivery share and ground water license
• Recycle dam
• This home is built with concrete tilt slabs, excellent insulation, warm in winter and cool in the summer months

Description:
Fantastic location
This three bedroom plus study family home is within excellent proximity to bushland, walking tracks and Scotts Oval and comprises formal lounge area plus meals/family room. The kitchen is functional in design and offers stainless steel dishwasher and cooker. Off the family room is a study/home office which has external access making it ideal for anyone working from home. The master bedroom has robes and ensuite with the remaining two bedrooms both offering built in robes and ceiling fans. The family bathroom has bath, shower and vanity. Externally there is an in-ground solar heated swimming pool, perfect for entertaining with family and friends, pergola/outdoor entertaining, paved court yard with pizza oven and firepit, double garage and 5kW solar electricity. This home is perfectly located and has lots to offer its new owners and wont disappoint.
